org.wildfly.swarm.cdi

Class UnmanagedInstance

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wildfly.swarm.cdi.UnmanagedInstance

  • public class UnmanagedInstance
extends Object
    Adapted from javax.enterprise.inject.spi.Unmanaged by supporting passing an instance to be injected into. This is necessary so that the Class of the instance can be loaded from a different ClassLoader than Weld is executing in.
    Author:
    Pete Muir, Ken Finnigan
